$date
  2026-06-07T00:00:00.000Z
$end
$version
  WaveCrux board demo fixture generator
$end
$comment
  Digilent Arty A7 out-of-box demo — individual per-bit signals.
  LED show: cylon / VU bar / chase / switch-mirror / expand / sparkle.
  Seven-seg: decoded readout — counter / accelerometer axes (all digits live). Buttons: staggered presses.
  Re-generate with `dart run tool/generate_board_demo_fixtures.dart`.
$end
$timescale 1 ns $end
$scope module top $end
$var wire 1 ! led0 $end
$var wire 1 " led1 $end
$var wire 1 # led2 $end
$var wire 1 $ led3 $end
$var wire 1 % led4 $end
$var wire 1 & led5 $end
$var wire 1 ' led6 $end
$var wire 1 ( led7 $end
$var wire 1 ) sw0 $end
$var wire 1 * sw1 $end
$var wire 1 + sw2 $end
$var wire 1 , sw3 $end
$var wire 1 - btn0 $end
$var wire 1 . btn1 $end
$var wire 1 / btn2 $end
$var wire 1 0 btn3 $end
$upscope $end
$enddefinitions $end
